    <briefdescription>
<para>Fixed-size, statically-allocated ring buffer. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Designed for ISR-safe single-producer / single-consumer use. The buffer is caller-owned — you provide the backing array and the <ref refid="structSYN__RingBuf" kindref="compound">SYN_RingBuf</ref> struct; the library never allocates memory.</para>
